description: [``botocore``] Feature - Adds support for Internet Protocol Version 6 (IPv6) on RDS database instances.
[``botocore``] Amazon CodeGuru Reviewer now supports suppressing recommendations from being generated on specific files and directories.
[``botocore``] Update the StartChangeRequestExecution, adding TargetMaps to the Runbook parameter
[``botocore``] AWS Elemental MediaConvert SDK nows supports creation of Dolby Vision profile 8.1, the ability to generate black frames of video, and introduces audio-only DASH and CMAF support.
[``botocore``] You can now inspect all request headers and all cookies. You can now specify how to handle oversize body contents in your rules that inspect the body.
